RTSAdmin Community Edition is an administration tool for managing RisingTide
Systems storage targets using the kernel LIO core target and compatible target
fabric modules. The rtsadmin CLI is built on top of the python configshell CLI
framework.

The latest version of this prgram might be obtained at:
http://www.risingtidesystems.com/git/

To run the CLI from this directory use:
sudo PYTHONPATH=. ./scripts/rtsadmin
